    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tiles of War is a turn-based strategy / tactics game, where you can capture every territory.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by timeless classics, Tiles of War takes tactics games to the next level by letting you capture all territories on the map! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick a side and use your units wisely to dominate the map, leading your faction to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Battle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Strategise and make the best move possible to wipe out your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e085bf1ff023387046254f3434e88efc.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e085bf1ff023387046254f3434e88efc.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e085bf1ff023387046254f3434e88efc.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><br><strong>Commanders</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each of the 18 commanders comes with a truly unique passive, small and big abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e19332e11726e326749e803c419677f1.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=784 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e19332e11726e326749e803c419677f1.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/e19332e11726e326749e803c419677f1.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Capture territories</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The entire map can be captured. Infantry can secure more territory by surrounding tiles, though enemy infantry can interrupt the process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/6f7a09073abc99a11b5e2b8fce3f5d59.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/6f7a09073abc99a11b5e2b8fce3f5d59.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/6f7a09073abc99a11b5e2b8fce3f5d59.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Campaign</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each faction has its own campaign to uncover what happens between the Humans, Undead, and Elves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/5b18299f91561d82e15300b6bfb524ec.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/5b18299f91561d82e15300b6bfb524ec.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/5b18299f91561d82e15300b6bfb524ec.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Skirmish</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">A variety of settings to customise your battles:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/9ff19e0867c7f9e3891b267a64884bd1.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/9ff19e0867c7f9e3891b267a64884bd1.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/9ff19e0867c7f9e3891b267a64884bd1.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Map generation, Custom maps, Fog of War, Etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>(Competitive) Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Fight the best of the best for a position on the global ranking system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/862cfd1c091352ef123127b4ea430cbd.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/862cfd1c091352ef123127b4ea430cbd.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/862cfd1c091352ef123127b4ea430cbd.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Map and Scenario editor</strong><br>Create custom maps and stories in our Map Editor </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/7218430c6642cb4c69aa25580cfd449d.poster.avif?t=1770559485\" width=960 height=540 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/7218430c6642cb4c69aa25580cfd449d.webm?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2354240/extras/7218430c6642cb4c69aa25580cfd449d.mp4?t=1770559485\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
